            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Hd1e108">Rubrica 30</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De peccato et peccatoribus consideratione religiosa</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
      ¶ De peccato et peccatoribus conside
      <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>ratione religiosa. Rubrica 30
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>PSalmista. i pslamus <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e125">Bea
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>tus vir qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>non abiit in consilio impiorum: et in via pec <!--49.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46" break="no"/>catorum non stetit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e139"> /
       <ref>psalmus. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e141">Qui diligit iniquita
        <lb ed="#V" n="47" break="no"/>tem odit animam suam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e148"> /
       <ref>36 psalmus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e150">Considerat peccator
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>iustum et querit mortificare eum: dominus autem non de
        <lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>relinquet eum in manibus eius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>
               ¶ <ref>Salomon in prouer. c. 23.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e162">Ne emuletur cor
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>tuum peccatores: sed in timore dei estote tota die:
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>quia habebis spem in nouissimo: et presto
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>latio tua non auferetur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e172">
               <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>
               ¶ <ref>Thobie hysto. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e176">Qui faciunt peccata et
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>iniquitatem: hostes sunt animae sue.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e182">
               <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>
               ¶ <ref>Iesus filius sirach in eccl. ca. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e186">Non adiicias
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>peccatum: et ne dicas miseratio dei magna est: mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>tudi peccatorum meorum miserebitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e194"> /
      <ref>c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e196">Non ze
        <lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>les gloriam et opes peccatoris: non enim scis quae
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>futura sit illius subuersio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e204">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
               ¶ <ref>Mattheus in euan. c. 19</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e208">Iesus dixit: Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>homicidium facies: non adulterabis: non facies <!--In print there is gap between 't' and 'e' in adulterabis-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>furtum: non falsum testimonium dices.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e217">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
               ¶ <ref>Ioannes in epistula. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e221">Si dixerimus quoniam peccatum
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>non habemus: ipsi nos seducimus: et veritas
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>in nobis non est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e229"> /
      <ref>ca. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e231">Omnis qui facit peccatum:
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>seruus peccati est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e237"> /
      <ref>c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e239"> Si ceci essetis: non
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>haberetis peccatum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e245"> /
      <ref>Idem epi i. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e247"> Omnis quae
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>facit peccatum et iniquitatem facit: et peccatum est ini
        <lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>quitas. Qui facit peccatum ex diabolo est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e255"> /
      <ref>c. 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e257"> <unclear>et fi.</unclear> Omnis iniquitas peccatum est: et est peccatum ad <!--move 'et fi.' to inside ref tag-->
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>mortem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e265"> /
       <ref>Idem epistola. 2. c. vnico.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e267">Qui male
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>facit non videt deum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e274">
               <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>
               ¶ <ref>Iudas alphei apostolus: qui fuit frater iacobi
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>apostoli epistola vnica. cap. 2. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e278">Peccatores
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>impii hi sunt: murmuratores: querulosi secundum
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>desideria sua ambulantes: et os illorum loqui
        <lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>tur superbiam: mirantes personas questus causa.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e290">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
               ¶ <ref>Iacobus apostolus epistola vnica. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e294">Peccatum cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>consummatum fuerit generat mortem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e300"> /
      <ref>c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e302">Sci
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>enti bonum facere et non facienti peccatum est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e308">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
               ¶ <ref>Paulus apostolus epistola. i. ad corinthios. ca. 10</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e312">Non potestis mense dei participes esse et
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>mense demoniorum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e320"> /
       <ref>c. 15.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e322">Stimulus mor
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>tis peccatum est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e328">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
               ¶ <ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum: libro 17 epistola
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>et.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e332">Omnibus crimen suum voluptati est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e339">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e343">/ Idem de moribus. Omne peccatum actio
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>est voluntaria.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e349">
               <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>
               ¶ <ref>Isidorus soliloquiorum li. 2. c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e353">Sepe occa <!--50.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="12-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1" break="no"/>sio peccandi voluntatem facit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e365">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>
               ¶ <ref>Mattheus vindocinensis in poetria: par
        <lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>ticula. i. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e369">Peccatum geminat peccantis
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>gloria: culpam. Diffamat fame dissipentis ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>nor.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-d1e379"> /
       <ref>c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de8596-Qd1e381">Uenialis est peccandi inciden
        <lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>tia: sed criminalis peccandi frequentia.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
